com.ibm.zrl.idmx.dm.structure
Class AttributeStructure

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.zrl.idmx.dm.structure.AttributeStructure

public class AttributeStructure
extends java.lang.Object

Attribute structures are used as part to a credential structure. In particular, they define the issuance mode, data type, name and the position within the credential (i.e., the public key index).
